## Prerequisites

- Node.js 18+ and npm
- Chrome or Firefox browser

## Installation

```bash
npm install
```

## Configuration

Update `config/wdio.config.ts` to configure your test environment:

```typescript
export const config: Options.Testrunner = {
  baseUrl: 'https://your-app.com',
  // ... other settings
};
```

## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
npm test

# Run in Chrome
npm run test:chrome

# Run in Firefox
npm run test:firefox

# Run in headless mode (CI/CD)
npm run test:headless
```

## Generate Reports

```bash
# Generate Allure report
npm run allure:generate

# Open Allure report
npm run allure:open
```

